  "description": "Burn-rate meter for AI coding agents. Surfaces quadratic session cost and reasoning-workspace drift; nudges curated handoffs at 50/75/90% via a bundled agent protocol so context resets at position 0 instead of /compact summarizing under pressure. Zero deps. Claude Code.",
